.nf
template<typename InputIterator> 
  result_type operator()(InputIterator first, InputIterator last) const;
.fi

.PP
Effects:
.RS 4
Attempts to dereference every iterator in the sequence
[first, last)\&.
.RE
.PP
Returns:
.RS 4
The result of the last successful iterator dereference\&.
.RE
.PP
Throws:
.RS 4
no_slots_error
if no iterators were successfully dereferenced, unless the template type of
last_value
is
void\&.
.RE
.RE

